# Notebooks to skip during sync.
# One pattern per line. Supports glob wildcards (* and ?).
# Matches against both notebook name and full path.
#
# Examples:
#   Kvitto*             # skip notebooks starting with "Kvitto"
#   /trash/*            # skip everything in trash
#   *.docx              # skip all docx imports

# Imported PDFs without handwriting (no .rm files)
System handover guidelines
Jira Align - Subscriptions Mission*
Financial Core Data Initiative
Payouts

# Personal folders
/Noter/*
/matildas/*
